Think of Apex as the â€œbrainâ€ behind your Salesforce components â€” when buttons are clicked, records updated, or logic applied, Apex defines what happens.

âš™ï¸ Where Apex Fits in Salesforce:
Layer	Description
UI Layer (Front-end)	Lightning pages, Lightning Web Components (LWC)
